description:
Lasting Finish 25HR is Rimmel London’s #1 skincare inspired foundation. Its long-lasting formula is infused with hyaluronic acid and vitamin E, helping to boost your skin with hydration so it appears fresh, plump and smooth.

Want a long-lasting foundation that also cares for your skin? Try Rimmel London’s #1 skincare inspired foundation - Lasting Finish 25HR. The long-lasting formula is infused with hyaluronic acid and vitamin E, helping to boost your skin with hydration so it appears fresh, plump and smooth. It blends seamlessly into your skin, concealing dark circles and imperfections. No need to worry about sweat, heat or humidity - your foundation stays flawless for up to 25 hours.
Apply a small amount - a little goes a long way - then sheer it out or build it up to full coverage with a beauty blender or a brush.


Long-Lasting Foundation with Hydration Boost

Infused with Hyaluronic Acid and Vitamin E

SPF 20

Full Coverage

Natural Finish
name: Rimmel Lasting Finish Full Coverage Foundation 103 True Ivory 30mL
